name: GongTimer
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: gong timer
des:
This skill is the basic timer for study, meditation, any scene that you don't want to hear loud alert when the time is up.
You can use like normal timer, the timer start and end with gong sound. 

Available command:
"Cancel"
"Stop"
"Pause"
"Resume"
"Next" (tell you how much time left)
"Help"
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
